  "changelog": "**Polygon 0.7.0 — full rebrand.** The workflow directory and every managed asset drop the `trellis` name.\n\n- Workflow dir `.trellis/` → `.polygon/` (renamed in place by `polygon update`, before anything else — your tasks/spec/workspace/journal move with it, zero data loss).\n- All skills/agents/commands `trellis-*` → `polygon-*` across every platform (`.claude/`, `.codex/`, `.agents/`, `.cursor/`, …).\n- Env vars `TRELLIS_*` → `POLYGON_*`; AGENTS.md managed-block markers `<!-- TRELLIS:START/END -->` → `<!-- POLYGON:START/END -->`.\n- CLI is `polygon` only; the `trellis` / `tl` aliases are gone.\n\nUpstream-merge compatibility is intentionally dropped from this release onward.",
